{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":988,"text":"These dragons from deep time\nare incredible creatures."},{"time":5701,"text":"They're bizzarre,"},{"time":7146,"text":"they're beautiful,"},{"time":8856,"text":"and there's very little\nwe know about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11841,"text":"These thoughts were going\nthrough my head"},{"time":14131,"text":"when I looked at the pages of\nmy first dinosaur book."},{"time":18574,"text":"I was about five years old at the time,"},{"time":21078,"text":"and I decided there and then\n"},{"time":23031,"text":"that I would become a paleontologist."},{"time":25876,"text":"Paleontology allowed me \nto combine my love for animals"},{"time":29213,"text":"with my desire to travel to \nfar-flung corners of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33941,"text":"And now, a few years later,\nI've led several expeditions"},{"time":36964,"text":"to the ultimate far-flung corner \non this planet, the Sahara."},{"time":42146,"text":"I've worked in the Sahara because\nI've been on a quest"},{"time":46195,"text":"to uncover new remains of\na bizarre, giant predatory dinosaur"},{"time":51300,"text":"called Spinosaurus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54451,"text":"A few bones of this animal\nhave been found"},{"time":57804,"text":"in the deserts of Egypt"},{"time":59184,"text":"and were described about 100 years ago\nby a German paleontologist."},{"time":64537,"text":"Unfortunately, all his Spinosaurus bones\nwere destroyed in World War II."},{"time":69485,"text":"So all we're left with are just\na few drawings and notes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73789,"text":"From these drawings,"},{"time":75050,"text":"we know that this creature, which lived \nabout 100 million years ago,"},{"time":78461,"text":"was very big,"},{"time":80012,"text":"it had tall spines on its back,\nforming a magnificent sail,"},{"time":83425,"text":"and it had long, slender jaws, \na bit like a crocodile,"},{"time":89542,"text":"with conical teeth,"},{"time":91760,"text":"that may have been used \nto catch slippery prey, like fish."},{"time":96647,"text":"But that was pretty much \nall we knew"},{"time":98704,"text":"about this animal for the next 100 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106563,"text":"My fieldwork took me to the border region\nbetween Morocco and Algeria,"},{"time":111365,"text":"a place called the Kem Kem."},{"time":113938,"text":"It's a difficult place to work in."},{"time":116251,"text":"You have to deal with sandstorms\nand snakes and scorpions,"},{"time":119940,"text":"and it's very difficult to find\ngood fossils there."},{"time":123084,"text":"But our hard work paid off."},{"time":125900,"text":"We discovered many incredible specimens."},{"time":128115,"text":"There's the largest dinosaur bone"},{"time":129867,"text":"that had ever been found\nin this part of the Sahara."},{"time":133475,"text":"We found remains of giant\npredatory dinosaurs,"},{"time":136969,"text":"medium-sized predatory dinosaurs,"},{"time":139632,"text":"and seven or eight different kinds\nof crocodile-like hunters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145231,"text":"These fossils were deposited\nin a river system."},{"time":148233,"text":"The river system was also home \nto a giant, car-sized coelacanth,"},{"time":152403,"text":"a monster sawfish,"},{"time":155863,"text":"and the skies over the river system\nwere filled with pterosaurs,"},{"time":159563,"text":"flying reptiles."},{"time":161591,"text":"It was a pretty dangerous place,"},{"time":163210,"text":"not the kind of place where you'd want\nto travel to if you had a time machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168159,"text":"So we're finding all these \nincredible fossils of animals"},{"time":171079,"text":"that lived alongside Spinosaurus,"},{"time":173769,"text":"but Spinosaurus itself proved\nto be very elusive."},{"time":176538,"text":"We were just finding bits and pieces"},{"time":178285,"text":"and I was hoping that we'd find\na partial skeleton at some point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183640,"text":"Finally, very recently,"},{"time":185357,"text":"we were able to track down a dig site"},{"time":188467,"text":"where a local fossil hunter found\nseveral bones of Spinosaurus."},{"time":193431,"text":"We returned to the site,\nwe collected more bones."},{"time":196291,"text":"And so after 100 years we finally\nhad another partial skeleton"},{"time":200364,"text":"of this bizarre creature."},{"time":202525,"text":"And we were able to reconstruct it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204196,"text":"We now know that \nSpinosaurus had a head"},{"time":206090,"text":"a little bit like a crocodile,"},{"time":207886,"text":"very different from other \npredatory dinosaurs,"},{"time":210081,"text":"very different from the T. rex."},{"time":212818,"text":"But the really interesting information\ncame from the rest of the skeleton."},{"time":217671,"text":"We had long spines,"},{"time":219004,"text":"the spines forming the big sail."},{"time":221632,"text":"We had leg bones, we had skull bones,"},{"time":223877,"text":"we had paddle-shaped feet, wide feet --"},{"time":227325,"text":"again, very unusual, no other\ndinosaur has feet like this --"},{"time":230140,"text":"and we think they may have been\nused to walk on soft sediment,"},{"time":233251,"text":"or maybe for paddling in the water."},{"time":235943,"text":"We also looked at the fine\nmicrostructure of the bone,"},{"time":239381,"text":"the inside structure of Spinosaurus bones,"},{"time":241377,"text":"and it turns out that they're\nvery dense and compact."},{"time":244136,"text":"Again, this is something we see in animals\nthat spend a lot of time in the water,"},{"time":247994,"text":"it's useful for buoyancy \ncontrol in the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251186,"text":"We C.T.-scanned all of our bones\nand built a digital Spinosaurus skeleton."},{"time":256559,"text":"And when we looked \nat the digital skeleton,"},{"time":258770,"text":"we realized that yes, this was\na dinosaur unlike any other."},{"time":263206,"text":"It's bigger than a T. rex,"},{"time":264805,"text":"and yes, the head has \"fish-eating\"\nwritten all over it,"},{"time":267530,"text":"but really the entire skeleton has\n\"water-loving\" written all over it --"},{"time":271629,"text":"dense bone, paddle-like feet,\nand the hind limbs are reduced in size,"},{"time":276464,"text":"and again, this is something\nwe see in animals"},{"time":278672,"text":"that spend a substantial amount \nof time in the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282711,"text":"So, as we fleshed out our Spinosaurus --"},{"time":286104,"text":"I'm looking at muscle attachments\nand wrapping our dinosaur in skin --"},{"time":290268,"text":"we realize that we're dealing\nwith a river monster,"},{"time":294148,"text":"a predatory dinosaur, bigger than T. rex,"},{"time":296477,"text":"the ruler of this ancient river of giants,"},{"time":299253,"text":"feeding on the many aquatic animals\nI showed you earlier on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302503,"text":"So that's really what makes this\nan incredible discovery."},{"time":305369,"text":"It's a dinosaur like no other."},{"time":306874,"text":"And some people told me, \"Wow,\nthis is a once-in-a-lifetime discovery."},{"time":310441,"text":"There are not many things left\nto discover in the world.\""},{"time":314803,"text":"Well, I think nothing could be \nfurther from the truth."},{"time":317975,"text":"I think the Sahara's \nstill full of treasures,"},{"time":320246,"text":"and when people tell me there are\nno places left to explore,"},{"time":323431,"text":"I like to quote a famous dinosaur hunter,\nRoy Chapman Andrews,"},{"time":327468,"text":"and he said, \"Always, there has been\nan adventure just around the corner --"},{"time":333084,"text":"and the world is still full of corners.\""},{"time":335896,"text":"That was true many decades ago"},{"time":337815,"text":"when Roy Chapman Andrews\nwrote these lines."},{"time":339857,"text":"And it is still true today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341839,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342727,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}